vote.title: A resolution ratifying the City Manager’s execution of an emergency service price agreement with BCFS Health and Human Services through an Interlocal Agreement with the City of San Antonio, for homeless shelter and dormitory management services related to COVID-19 for the Office of Homeless Solutions - Estimated amount of $75,409.04 - Financing: General Fund
